        "original": "え？怖い怖い！",
        "english": "Eh? Scary, scary!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:32.000",
        "end": "03:33.800",
        "original": "ミオちゃんが怖がっている！",
        "english": "Mio-chan is scared!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:34.600",
        "end": "03:39.100",
        "original": "嘘でしょ？何これ？これ何なんだろう、気持ち悪い...",
        "english": "No way... What is this? What is it? It's gross...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:41.800",
        "end": "03:45.300",
        "original": "何これ、何これ！怖い怖い怖い！",
        "english": "What is this, what is this! Scary, scary, scary!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:50.000",
        "end": "03:53.600",
        "original": "分かった分かったじゃないの、その反応。",
        "english": "That reaction doesn't look like you understand at all.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:55.200",
        "end": "03:57.300",
        "original": "Time's up!",
        "english": "Time's up!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "on_screen_text"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:55.500",
        "end": "03:58.200",
        "original": "何？いや、いやーー！",
        "english": "What? No, noooo!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:00.700",
        "end": "04:02.800",
        "original": "大げさにやってるでしょ？",
        "english": "You're exaggerating, aren't you?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:06.800",
        "end": "04:08.700",
        "original": "ちょっと行ってみて行ってみて、これちょっと。",
        "english": "You should try it too. Really.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:09.500",
        "end": "04:10.500",
        "original": "あ、次AZKi？",
        "english": "Oh, AZKi's next?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:10.500",
        "end": "04:11.800",
        "original": "AZKi先輩、頑張って。",
        "english": "Good luck, AZKi-senpai.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:12.300",
        "end": "04:14.800",
        "original": "AZKiの挑戦",
        "english": "AZKi's Challenge",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "on_screen_text"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:15.500",
        "end": "04:16.800",
        "original": "スタート！",
        "english": "Start!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:17.000",
        "end": "04:19.200",
        "original": "うわあああ！やっぱそうだよね！",
        "english": "Uwaaaaa! I knew it!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:19.200",
        "end": "04:20.500",
        "original": "行ってみてよ。",
        "english": "Give it a try.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:24.400",
        "end": "04:26.200",
        "original": "その反応になるって。",
        "english": "See? That's the reaction you'll get.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:26.500",
        "end": "04:28.400",
        "original": "もしゃもしゃしてます。",
        "english": "It's kind of fuzzy/shaggy.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:30.100",
        "end": "04:31.400",
        "original": "ヒントは？",
        "english": "Any hints?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:32.300",
        "end": "04:35.000",
        "original": "もしゃもしゃ...",
